snippet.title: FuryDough - Official Steam Next Fest Trailer (October 2024)
snippet.description:
Play and Wishlist:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2350880/FuryDough/

FuryDough is an action roguelite where donuts are everywhere, and you will hate them. 
Break through mazes, fight with a crowd of zany doughy adversaries, find and destroy Dough Mixers. 
This is not a sweet dream, but a real nightmare.
